Hey <@U031JS3RF0V> 
Sorry if I am too late to this, I have attended GrowthX as well and I didn't find it to be super relevant either to B2B or SaaS. 
It's great for PLG though, so if that's something you would like to learn GrowthX is a great pick. 

Other reasons to join GrowthX - 
1. Probably one of the only cohorts that is full of value and less fluff and parties in Goa every 2nd month rather than. 
2. Amazing network of folks spread across the entire B2C and a little of B2B landscape in the country.
